                        >
                            Yes. As long as you have valid status (including
                            Maintained Status) at the time of registration and
                            application, you are eligible. However, if your
                            status restoration is rejected, your BC PNP
                            application will also be cancelled.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details
                        class="group bg-slate-50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 open:bg-white open:ring-1 open:ring-indigo-100 open:shadow-md transition-all"
