                                nomination?</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 text-indigo-500"
                                >▼</span
                            >
                        </summary>
                        <div
                            class="mt-4 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 animate-fadeIn"
                        >
                            If you lose your job, you must inform BC PNP
                            immediately. If you have valid status, you may be
                            given a short window to find a new qualifying
                            employer. If your work permit was "Closed" (tied to
                            that employer), you cannot work anywhere else until
                            you get a new permit.
                        </div>
                    </details>
